 
query_see_octarine          Discworld living help           query_see_octarine

Name
     query_see_octarine - can the object see the colour octarine.

Syntax
     int query_see_octarine();

Description
     Returns 1 if the object can see the colour octarine, or 0 if they can't.
     Seeing octarine will allow the object to receive descriptions specified
     by the octarine_mess property.                                  

See also
     octarine_mess         
